<div class="container">
<div class="contact row" >
    <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 cardInfo">
        <p>Vous pouvez nous contacter :<br>
            <span class="infoContact">par mail: garageparrot@gmail.com<br>
            Tel:  09.66.34.56.12</span><br>
